definitions.definition: ( rare ) Of or relating to an ounce , or an inch , especially to letters printed an inch high.

definitions.definition: Of or relating to a majuscule style of writing with unjoined , rounded letters , originally used in the 4th–9th centuries.

main_definition: Of or relating to a majuscule style of writing with unjoined , rounded letters , originally used in the 4th–9th centuries.
